title: GEGeek Tech Toolkit 10.1
description:
A Complete Collection of over 600 Tech Related Free Programs/Suites, all accessible from one Menu Launcher Utility. There's even a program to update all the essential programs automatically, all contained on a Flash Drive for travel. You can now totally customize the entire program to make it your own. You can add/delete programs, change the interface layout, whatever you want to match your own personal needs or style. You can even run programs as Admin on the fly. Now with Windows 10 Quick Configuration, Executable, Registry Mods, all accessible right from the menu and adding more all the time.  
Over 5 gigs of programs from a < 25MB download
